{
  "texts": [
    "LLMs like ChatGPT and GPT-4 have immense potential to improve human life across the board.",
    "But, there is also a significant risk of systemic harms being ingrained deeper due to their use (FOL-Institute, 2023).",
    "The most urgent need is to understand the issues and measure their degrees in a comprehensive manner.",
    "This will allow us to gauge the potential impact on society and prioritize future development that limits the harm caused.",
    "Our work is a step in that direction for the potential harm of bias."
  ]
}